snippets.title: LivestreamService createChannel Sample
snippets.description: Creates a channel with the provided unique ID in the specified region.

snippets.title: LivestreamService listChannels Sample
snippets.description: Returns a list of all channels in the specified region.

snippets.title: LivestreamService getChannel Sample
snippets.description: Returns the specified channel.

snippets.title: LivestreamService deleteChannel Sample
snippets.description: Deletes the specified channel.

snippets.title: LivestreamService updateChannel Sample
snippets.description: Updates the specified channel.

snippets.title: LivestreamService startChannel Sample
snippets.description: Starts the specified channel. Part of the video pipeline will be created only when the StartChannel request is received by the server.

snippets.title: LivestreamService stopChannel Sample
snippets.description: Stops the specified channel. Part of the video pipeline will be released when the StopChannel request is received by the server.

snippets.title: LivestreamService createInput Sample
snippets.description: Creates an input with the provided unique ID in the specified region.

snippets.title: LivestreamService listInputs Sample
snippets.description: Returns a list of all inputs in the specified region.

snippets.title: LivestreamService getInput Sample
snippets.description: Returns the specified input.

snippets.title: LivestreamService deleteInput Sample
snippets.description: Deletes the specified input.

snippets.title: LivestreamService updateInput Sample
snippets.description: Updates the specified input.

snippets.title: LivestreamService createEvent Sample
snippets.description: Creates an event with the provided unique ID in the specified channel.

snippets.title: LivestreamService listEvents Sample
snippets.description: Returns a list of all events in the specified channel.

snippets.title: LivestreamService getEvent Sample
snippets.description: Returns the specified event.

snippets.title: LivestreamService deleteEvent Sample
snippets.description: Deletes the specified event.

snippets.title: LivestreamService listClips Sample
snippets.description: Returns a list of all clips in the specified channel.

snippets.title: LivestreamService getClip Sample
snippets.description: Returns the specified clip.

snippets.title: LivestreamService createClip Sample
snippets.description: Creates a clip with the provided clip ID in the specified channel.

snippets.title: LivestreamService deleteClip Sample
snippets.description: Deletes the specified clip job resource. This method only deletes the clip job and does not delete the VOD clip stored in the GCS.

snippets.title: LivestreamService createAsset Sample

snippets.title: LivestreamService deleteAsset Sample

snippets.title: LivestreamService listAssets Sample
snippets.description: Returns a list of all assets in the specified region.
